<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    .main-container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: auto;
        margin-top: 50px;
        padding: 0 0 50px 50px;
        border: 5px solid black;
        border-radius: 5px;
        /* CSS GRID LAYOUT */
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        grid-template-rows: auto;
        grid-gap: 5px;
        background-color: silver;
        border-color: mediumvioletred;
    }

    .center {
        margin: auto;
        width: 200%;
        padding: 10px;
    }
</style>
<div class="main-container">
    <div class="center">
        <h2 class="">About Us</h2>

        <br />

        <label class="center">
            Team America is open again including summer camps.
            Our camps are kept to small numbers of players.
            Coach Jonny runs the camp.
            Coach Jonny has completed his Red Cross first aid certification and is tested regularly for Covid.
            When a player comes to camp the player must wear masks, use hand sanitizers as directed and have their temperature taken before entering each day.
        </label>
    </div>
</div>

